## Limitations

This analysis is limited by the availability of data and the subjective nature of economic interpretations. The sources used provide a range of perspectives, but they may not cover all aspects of Reaganomics comprehensively. Additionally, the long-term effects of these policies continue to be debated, and new data or interpretations could alter the conclusions drawn in this report.